// Esolang tradition demo: counter loop (Brainfuck joke, Bark edition).
//
// In Brainfuck, +++++. means: add 1 five times (+), then print the cell (.).
// We don't run Brainfuck here. Same idea: loop, increment, show the result.
//
// Run: ./gradlew run --args="examples/woof/counter-tradition.woof"

I have a corgi.

while she sniffs less toys than 8 then
    she finds a toy
bury

bark "The count is:"
she woof how many toys she has
